Text: Lost Creek crop damage Cc Attached isthe form of release letter Merrick intends to use in connection with its payment of minor crop damage on the Lost Creek pipeline project Please let me know if you have any comments with respect to the form of the releaseMerrick intends to send payment with the letter on January Thank you Phil Rouse Jack Corbett doc
